	<h1>
		Trufab Stainless Steel Fabrication</h1>
	<br />
	With 30 years experience in the sheetmetal world, Trufab are the UK leading stainless steel fabrication engineers in the industry. Specialising in the manufacture of high quality fabrications in stainless steel and other exotic alloys, suited to dynamic design requirements of today. We have a unique total software package designed in-house, which enables a rapid update of customer contracts.<br />
	&nbsp;<br />
	Complementing our software package are a team of well-motivated managers, who are dedicated to man-hour management and total quality. With up to the minute CNC fabrication and CNC machinery plant technology, combined with traditional skills we are well prepared to meet the complex demands of today&#39;s industry<br />
	<br />
	<h2>
		Our Vision</h2>
	<br />
	In the first instance there has to be a vision, a dream. It&#39;s where you want to go, what you want to be. Our vision is simple, to become the dominant player in the high quality stainless steel fabrication industry. To keep improving quality and reducing costs by marrying traditional skills together with the latest in high-tech equipment we are able to offer the complete one stop solution.</div>
